PH213-319 are arranged chronologically. PH320-PH416 are not arranged
                 chronologically. The inclusive months are January; March-July;
                 September-October, and December 1963.

Ethiopia: performance celebrating Kenya's Independence. The performance
              includes a series of folk music and dances: Flower Picking Song; Gurage folk
              dance; Buna coffee plantation song dances; Issa & Ougaden folk dance;
              Gondor folk-song; Arussi folk dance; Swahili Amharic dance; Gemu Gofa weavers;
              Wolamo folk dance for men and women, and the Tigre folk dance.
